- Each short description should be at least 2 to 4 sentences that summarize the topic and build on the title without repeating it.
- Put the most relevant language and keywords in the first 155 characters.
- Summarize the key information in the topic.
- Use active voice.
- Highlight the customer benefit or user's main job.
- Use simple, concise, declarative sentences.
- Avoid self-referential phrases like "This topic describes..."
